data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This program is used to add / remove the default folders from "This PC" on Windows 10, Windows 8.1, Server 2012 R2, Server 2016.
This program works by modifying the registry. Please see my website for specific regkeys that are modified.
I have tested this on x64 Windows 10 1703, Server 2012 R2.
